      "post_id" : 6490053,
      "comment_id" : 23987540,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "+1, afaik - this is the ONLY post that actually answers the question.  YES there is a standard order as dictated by Oracle and Sun: 1. public comment, 2. class, 3. internal comment, 4. static data, 5. instance data, 6. ctors, 7. methods, and within each section group logically, not by accessibility."
